{"tid":2410002,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電影「Us」 係咪最完美示範 女權 + 黑人 既最佳電影","createTime":"2021-02-16T09:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T10:14:56.000Z","uid":42246,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85519066d849478dbea77403d1d702647503cf55","tid":2410002,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8hy1br.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8hy1br.png&h=e2b2e950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmR4oqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmR4oqT.jpg&h=a8a534e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角團全黑人冇白人<br />\n主角團+主奸角團都係黑人 一個白人都唔侵佢玩<br />\n第一個死既係白人 （唔再係黑人第一個死）<br />\n唔計分身外 死既都係白人 冇黑人<br />\n成套戲女主角為重心<br />\n個黑人男主角勁撚大隻成座山咁 但勁撚廢 勁撚蠢<br />\n要個黑人老婆carry 唔係個黑人弱智老公死撚左十次<br />\n黑人女人渣車好勁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最低死都係劇情 <br />\n個個位都停電 + 黑人做戲=眼前一黑 唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講上邊d黑人女權野<br />\n班地底人想用把較剪統治世界又係搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個結局多bug到 話出去就出去個原女主角點解要留係地底咁耐 變埋做一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a78a97cd83fc9fc7eebb9afc4c33925832241c","tid":2410002,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650e018adfb8361f577b8066bda8628be35a66dd","tid":2410002,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"cited